    <property>
      <answer>To add a pedigree chart to a patient record, enter //Edit// mode and navigate to the //Family history and pedigree// section of the record. Click on //Draw Pedigree// to enter the Pedigree editor. You will have the option of selecting a starting template; new nodes and relationships can be added within the editor. Once you have completed editing the pedigree chart, click //Save// before closing.</answer>
